<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA523_03_IH_0005_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema523_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_03_ih_0005">
      <section class="title type2" lang="y">
        <h2 data-head="5" class="is_star2">두 사각형은 서로 합동입니다. 사각형 ㄱㄴㄷㄹ의 둘레가 40 ㎝일 때, 변 ㄴㄷ의 길이는몇 ㎝인지 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box align_center justify_center">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA523_03_IH/0005_01.png" alt="" />
            <span class="text text1">4 ㎝</span>
            <span class="text text2">13 ㎝</span>
            <span class="text text3">11 ㎝</span>
          </div>
          <div class="input_area flex align_center gap_10 ml_60">
            <span>(</span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="12 " text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span>㎝)</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">
                  합동인 두 도형에서 대응변의 길이는 각각 같으므로 <br />(변 ㄱㄹ)=(변 ㅇㅅ)=11 ㎝,<br />
                  (변 ㄹㄷ)=(변 ㅅㅂ)=13 ㎝입니다.<br />
                  사각형 ㄱㄴㄷㄹ의 둘레가 40 ㎝이므로 (변 ㄴㄷ) =40-4-11-13=12 (㎝)입니다.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
